h4. Environment
Git Version: 1.9.4, 1.9.1
OS: Windows 8.1, Ubuntu 14.04
Path tested:
{noformat}
* C:\\PROGRA~2\\libexec\\git-core
* C:\\PROGRA~2\\libexec
* C:\\PROGRA~2\\libexec\\git-core\\http-backend.exe
